---
// src/components/Cta.astro
---
<section class='cta-section'>
    <div class='container'>
        <div class='cta-card'>
            <!-- Elemento decorativo de luz de fondo (Glow) -->
            <div class="cta-glow"></div>
            
            <div class='cta-content'>
                <span class='eyebrow'>El siguiente paso</span>
                <h2>¿Listo para construir<br />tu futuro digital?</h2>
                <p>Deja de perder clientes por culpa de una web lenta o con diseño genérico. Hablemos sobre tu proyecto y descubramos cómo podemos ayudarte a dominar tu mercado.</p>
                <div class="cta-actions">
                    <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-accent btn-large">Iniciar Proyecto</a>
                    <a href="/servicios" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">Explorar Servicios</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .cta-section {
        padding: clamp(60px, 10vh, 120px) 0;
        background: var(--bg);
        position: relative;
    }
    
    .cta-card {
        position: relative;
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--surface) 30%, transparent);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px);
        padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem) clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        text-align: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        isolation: isolate;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }
    html[data-theme='light'] .cta-card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    /* Brillo de fondo animado */
    .cta-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 80%;
        height: 80%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 30%, transparent) 0%, transparent 70%);
        z-index: -1;
        filter: blur(60px);
        border-radius: 50%;
        animation: pulseGlow 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        pointer-events: none;
    }
    @keyframes pulseGlow {
        0% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.6; }
        100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.3) rotate(15deg); opacity: 1; }
    }

    .cta-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .eyebrow {
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 15%, transparent);
        color: var(--accent);
        padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        display: inline-block;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 30%, transparent);
    }
    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        line-height: 1.05;
        color: var(--fg);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .cta-content p {
        font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
        color: #86868b;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .cta-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn-large {
        padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .btn-outline {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--fg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 100px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
        background: var(--surface);
        border-color: var(--fg);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .cta-actions {
            flex-direction: column;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-large, .btn-outline {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
    }
</style>
